 "remarks": "Beautifully updated 4/5 bedroom 4 1/2 bath residence offering a turnkey lifestyle with the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless character, privately set on 1.95 serene, park-like acres. A circular driveway welcomes you to a fenced yard with a beautifully sited pool, expansive entertaining patio and gently rolling grassy knolls creating a peaceful, private retreat. Designed for both everyday living and entertaining, the home features generous, light filled spaces throughout. A first floor guest suite provides ideal flexibility, while the upper level includes a spacious primary suite and 3 additional bedrooms. Hardwood floors, two staircases, abundant storage, a separate pantry with extensive cabinetry and custom closets enhance comfort and function. A versatile main-level space offers a game/ family room or potential kitchen expansion. Distinctive living and dining rooms each feature fireplaces, and the living room is further enhanced by custom built-ins. Move-in ready, this special property delivers space, privacy and an elevated lifestyle in an idyllic setting. Greenwich taxes $17,388 Stamford taxes $300",
